title: The Prodigy
description:
The Prodigy started back in 1990 as a house band but later went on to experiment with both punkier style. Originally it was only music and beats band moving to full songs in the later records.

This are all five records and one extended re release plus 13 singles and one EP full singles.

Music For The Jilted Generation (1994)
The Fat Of The Land (1997)
The Dirtchamber Sessions Volume One (1999)
